%N A395357 The completed spiral of black and red knights (as in A392177, A392178, A395355) read in order, with +n indicating a black knight, -n a red knight, and 0 (except for the initial 0, which is special) an unoccupied square.
%C A395357 A395355 shows the spiral in the order in which it is filled in, whereas the present sequence shows the spiral after it has been filled in.
